name: Golden tiger
description: GDTE golden tiger is a decentralized and extremely deflationary currency based on the currency security ecological chain. The liquidity mine pool is permanently locked. 6% will be deducted from each transfer transaction on the GdTe chain, of which 3% will be added to the capital pool to provide liquidity, 1% will be invested in the black hole address in real time, and 2% will be allocated to other holders outside the black hole address in real time.
